     7→ * @param {number} value - The tile's internal value
     8→ * @param {string|null} specialType - Special tile type: "freeswap", "sticky_freeswap",
     9→ *                                     "freeswap_horizontal", "freeswap_vertical", "hammer", "halver", or null
    10→ * @param {Object} options - Additional options
